    {
      "id": "el_30",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 580,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: B faces Q -> same column pos 3\nStep 2: A to B's right (facing S=leftward)\nStep 3: A at R1-P2\n\n  Row1(S): _ A B _  (face South)\n           1 2 3 4\n  Row2(N): _ ? Q _  (face North)\n\nTRICK:\nOpposite = same column, other row.\nRight/Left depends on FACING direction.\nFacing S: right appears as left on diagram.\n\nAnswer: Person at R2-P2 is opposite A ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
