        "type_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: B faces Q -> same column pos 3\nStep 2: A to B's right (facing S=leftward)\nStep 3: A at R1-P2\n\n  Row1(S): _ A B _  (face South)\n           1 2 3 4\n  Row2(N): _ ? Q _  (face North)\n\nTRICK:\nOpposite = same column, other row.\nRight/Left depends on FACING direction.\nFacing S: right appears as left on diagram.\n\nAnswer: Person at R2-P2 is opposite A ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
