    {
      "id": "el_35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 994,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A is 3 left(CW) of D -> pos 4\nStep 2: B opposite A -> pos 4+4 = pos 8\nStep 3: C right(Anti-CW) of B -> pos 7\nStep 4: Opposite D(1) = 1+4 = pos 5\n\n       D(1)\n    B(8)   (2)\n   C(7)  o  (3)\n    (6)    A(4)\n       (5)\n\nTRICK:\nOpposite = current + N/2\nFacing center: Left=CW, Right=Anti-CW\n\nAnswer: Person at Pos 5 is opposite D ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
