    {
      "id": "el_45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 978,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A at short side = P1\nStep 2: B 2nd left(CW) of A -> P3\nStep 3: E opposite A -> P5\nStep 4: P3 opposite -> P7\n\n     B -- P3 -- P4\nA   |             |  E\n     P8 -- P7 -- P6\n\nTRICK:\nNumber seats CW. Opposite = across table.\nFor 8 seats: opposite = pos + 4 (mod 8)\n\nAnswer: Person at P7 is opposite B ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
