    {
      "id": "el_65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1816,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: B at pos 5 (right end)\nStep 2: C not at ends -> pos 2,3,4\nStep 3: A < C < D < E < B (chain)\nStep 4: A=1, C=2, D=3, E=4, B=5\n\n  A  C  D  E  B\n  1  2  3  4  5\n\nTRICK:\nFix endpoints first (B=5).\nChain inequalities to order the rest.\n\nAnswer: A, C, D, E, B ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
